|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130303051623/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2019%20%5B1927%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>2010年有教友421,820名，佔轄區總人口百分之16.3。由198名司鐸名管理106個堂區。現任教區主教為{{link-de|斯德望·安多尼·皮爾萊|Stephen Antony Pillai}}，榮休主教為{{link-en|毅華·安布魯瓦茲|Yvon Ambroise}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 17.01.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/01/17/190117b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715171409/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/01/17/190117b.html |archivedate=2019-07-15 |language=en |date=2019-01-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

